songs.title: Heaven’s Gates*
songs.lyrics:
[Lyrics from Snippet]

[Intro]
Real life
Get high
(Hahahaha)

[Chorus]
Real life, Drugs high
Good life, Feel right
You’re my [?]
You can watch, you can’t hide
Real life, Drugs high
Cool life, Drugs high
You’re right it’s best
That you came

[Post Chorus]
It is [?]
Fight for the control
Nobody knows
[?]
Fight for the control
Don’t anyone know, you don’t really wanna know

[Verse]
Money gives happiness? Cap!
Bitches got faithfulness? Cap!
And drugs only make it worse? Cap!
I pop a perk then I take me a nap
Take a sip of the syrup so I could go relapse
Bitch I’m ready for war when the demons attack, hell yeah, believe that
One to the face, don’t fucking hesitate
Bitch I’m high as heaven gates
Ain’t no coming down
One to the face, don’t fucking hesitate
Bitch I’m high as heaven gates
Ain’t no coming down, coming down (Down)
Bitch I’m high as heaven gates
Ain’t no coming down, coming down (Down)
